entries.title_d: The SpyNet commander you rescued have requested that we patrol the area and make sure none of the Blacklights are following him. We will provide you with patrol coordinates.
entries.title: Dantooine system: Patrol Blacklight Pirate Sector.
entries.split_quest_alert: Brother Ezkiel: < Stay on the alert, pilot. Our sensors detect enemy ships incoming. >
entries.quest_patrol_d: We will upload new patrol coordinates to your nav computer as you reach them. Proceed as planned.
entries.quest_location_d: You are on the edge of the Blacklight infested area but they are sneaky and may launch an ambush so stay alert.
